Skins.BgDescription: A uniform bestowed by Ju√© when Jiyan was appointed general. Its design is based on the standard uniform of the Midnight Rangers. The turquoise coat billows when the wind rises, like a flag that rallies his fellow soldiers. Made of tough materials, it's resistant to wear and tear, much like the enduring mountains of Jinzhou.

Skills.SkillDescribe:
Basic Attack

Perform up to 5 consecutive attacks, dealing Aero DMG.


Heavy Attack

Consume Stamina to thrust forward, dealing Aero DMG.


Heavy Attack: Windborne Strike

Hold Basic Attack during Heavy Attack to cast Windborne Strike after Heavy Attack ends, dealing Aero DMG.


Heavy Attack: Abyssal Slash

Release Basic Attack during Heavy Attack to cast Abyssal Slash after Heavy Attack ends, dealing Aero DMG.


Mid-Air Attack

Consume Stamina to perform a Plunging Attack while in mid-air, dealing Aero DMG.
After performing the Plunging Attack, use Basic Attack to perform a follow-up attack, dealing Aero DMG.


Mid-Air Attack: Banner of Triumph

After casting Heavy Attack Windborne Strike or Resonance Skill Windqueller in mid-air, Jiyan can perform a mid-air attack, dealing Aero DMG.


Dodge Counter

Use Basic Attack after a successful Dodge to attack the target, dealing Aero DMG.

Dash forward a certain distance, dealing Aero DMG.


Can be cast in the air.

After releasing Emerald Storm - Prelude, Jiyan enters Qingloong Mode.


Qingloong Mode

Jiyan has increased resistance to interruption.
Basic Attack, Heavy Attack and Dodge Counter are replaced with Heavy Attack Lance of Qingloong.


Heavy Attack: Lance of Qingloong

Perform up to 3 consecutive attacks, dealing Aero DMG, considered as Heavy Attack DMG.
After casting the Intro Skill Tactical Strike, Jiyan's ATK is increased by 10% for 15s.
When Jiyan's attacks hit a target, Jiyan's Crit. DMG is increased by 12% for 8s.
Jiyan pierces the target in mid-air, dealing Aero DMG.

When casting Resonance Skill Windqueller, if Jiyan has 30 or more "Resolve", he consumes 30 "Resolve" to increase the DMG of this Resonance Skill Windqueller by 20%.
When Jiyan is in Qingloong Mode, DMG of Resonance Skill Windqueller is increased by 20% and no longer consumes "Resolve".


Resonance Liberation: Emerald Storm - Finale

When casting Resonance Liberation Emerald Storm - Prelude, if Jiyan has 30 "Resolve" or more, he will consume 30 "Resolve" to cast Emerald Storm - Finale, dealing Aero DMG, considered as Heavy Attack DMG.
Emerald Storm: Finale can be cast in mid-air at low altitude.


Resolve

Jiyan can hold up to 60 Resolve.
Jiyan gains "Resolve" when his Normal Attack Lone Lance hits the target.
Jiyan gains "Resolve" when the Intro Skill Tactical Strike hits the target.
"Resolve" will gradually decrease if Jiyan does not hit a target within 15s.

When the incoming Resonator's Heavy Attack hits a target, Jiyan will summon a lance to launch a coordinated attack, dealing Aero DMG equal to 313.40% of Jiyan's ATK. This attack lasts for 8s and can be triggered once every 1s, up to 2 times.

TalentDoc.Title: Resonance Evaluation Report
TalentDoc.Content:
Evaluation Basis: [Resonance Assessment 2141-G]

Resonator Jiyan's Forte-Awakening was observed at Camp Overwatch located in Desorock Highland. This event was characterized by the accumulation of air currents around his body, forming a distinctive lance.

Jiyan bears a distinctive Tacet Mark situated atop his dorsal ridge. Post-Awakening observations found some growths that resemble Loong scale on his left jaw. No indications of progressive expansion have been detected.

Resonator Jiyan possesses the ability to manipulate wind energy, which he can channel into a "Qingloong" that aids him in battle. Additionally, he possesses exceptional perception and leadership skills, utilizing his connection to the winds to gather and analyze battlefield information with astonishing accuracy. Empirical testing has shown an impressive accuracy rate of 99.12% in evaluating dynamic situations.
Jiyan's Resonance Spectrum Pattern shows no resemblance to known samples. The cause of his Awakening remains unknown.

Analysis of test samples has revealed a non-convergent Rabelle's Curve with a steep rise in its middle section. Resonator Jiyan is thereby classified as a Mutant Resonator.

TalentCertification.Title: Overclock Diagnostic Report
TalentCertification.Content:
The waveform graph for Resonator Jiyan shows non-periodic rectangular pulse fluctuations, with sustained peak values during specific time intervals. These waveforms demonstrate rapid and substantial changes within a short temporal span. There are two distinct waveforms identified, each with exceptionally high peak values.

Resonant Criticality: Relatively high. Resonator Jiyan's frequency displays high stability with a low risk of Overclocking.

No history of Overclocking has been documented. Routine examinations and counseling are recommended.

Stories.Title: The Unyielding Will
Stories.Content:
Shortly after Jiyan's appointment as the Midnight Ranger's general, an unexpected Tacet Discord Outbreak occurred. It was during this battle that he suspected the Threnodian's resurrection.

As the weary soldiers recovered from a fierce battle on the frontline, they were greeted by an ominous sight: shadow ravens circling above and swarms of Tacet Discords charging towards their position at the Norfall Barrens and Desorock Highland pass.

The outnumbered army knew that failure to defend this stronghold could spell doom for the entire Huanglong.

Even seasoned veterans had never faced a crisis as urgent as this one. Amidst the chaos, Jiyan alone remained composed.

"All of you. Prepare to fight."

"Absurd! If we lose now, it's truly over. We can still retreat and protect the city!"

"Choose now: stand with courage, seize our chance. Or run and face defeat. For centuries, the Midnight Rangers have held this pass without retreat. Or do you prefer to go down in history as cowards?"

The veterans left, their emotions ranging from disappointment to rage.

Jiyan's resolve remained unshaken. He carefully studied real-time images from monitoring devices and noticed a connection between the Tacet Discords and the shadow ravens above. Quickly summoning the other commanders in the military, Jiyan devised a plan and led their coordinated army to face the enemy head-on. With precision, they used Sound Emulators set in a narrow valley to emit the shadow raven's frequency. As he expected, the Tacet Discords were drawn towards the sound, allowing for their easy capture.

Meanwhile, the Midnight Rangers stationed at Norfall Barrens were instructed to join hands with their comrades in the Desorock Highland, and carry out a pincer attack on the Tacet Discords. In the midst of a sandstorm, Jiyan bravely fought off hordes of enemies, paving the way for his fellow soldiers with unmatched strength.

The Tacet Mark on Jiyan's nape was flickering, a sign of Forte overexertion, but he pressed on. His Qingloong flew high in the sky like a proud banner of resolution, never once faltering to the ground.

Stories.Title: The Reason to Fight
Stories.Content:
Jiyan is the youngest general in the Midnight Rangers' history. He is the Qingloong that everyone looks up to, and the invincible warrior no enemy stands any chance against. However, at some point, Jiyan became haunted by a recurring nightmare.

In that dream, the city of Jinzhou was engulfed in flames and consumed by Tacet Discords. The monsters raged on, feeding on the frequencies of the dead. Chaotic sounds echoed throughout the city, creating a symphony of destruction.

On the flame-lit battlefield, a lone figure fought relentlessly with a lance in hand. Each swing tore through the air. One, two, three... Hundreds of thousands of Tacet Discords fell under his fierce and restless strikes.

Despite his best efforts, the man could not quell the endless swarm of Tacet Discords ravaging the land. Day after day, year after year, he fought in vain until he was the sole survivor on a desolate battlefield. The Tacet Discords transformed into his fallen comrades, encircling and closing in on him.

"That's a clueless kid! How can we trust him with our lives?"

"You said you would protect us... but why?"

"Jiyan, what on earth are you fighting for?"

Despite being known for his calm and decisive nature, few were aware of the nightmares that would sometimes jolt him awake, haunted by the voices of the dead.

As the general, it was Jiyan's duty to safeguard not only the borders, but also the entirety of his nation. Every move he made and every plan he enacted carried immense responsibility and consequence.

This is why he seems to be always frowning, thinking, and planning ahead. One day, perhaps, he will finally turn around and answer those questions from the dead.

He fights for the living, and for the deceased.

Stories.Title: Silent Caretaker
Stories.Content:
Strange things do happen in the Midnight Rangers' camps.

A soldier with a knee injury received specialized pain relief patches from the medics each time the seasons changed, despite the fact that he never told anyone about it.

Another soldier, previously inattentive during training, learned a few days later that the Midnight Rangers' General Affairs Department had paid for his mother's surgery.

When the logistics department was short on funds, it received a budget increase notice for the next quarter before any budget request was officially made.

Regardless of the size or age of the problem, there is always someone present to provide timely solutions when they are needed most. Just as a gentle rain quenches parched soil, this person carefully orchestrates aid and ensures that no area goes without assistance.

"Team 3's captain obviously had difficulties using his left leg during the drill. I went through his operation records, and it seems to stem from his prolonged exposure to the swamp during one of the previous missions. Pass along this prescription to the medics. They'll know what to do."

"Transfer some money to this account in the name of the General Affairs Department. Debit my account for the funding."

"I remember there has been a 20% increase in the number of recruits this year. Verify this with the Logistics. If confirmed, adjust next quarter's budget accordingly."

This is Jiyan, whose ruthlessness is reserved for enemies, while his tenderness is shown to comrades.

Stories.Title: What's Inside His Gourd?
Stories.Content:
When asked about his childhood, Jiyan recalls a plethora of memories: the smell of medicine, the bright lights of the operating room, the sound of medical equipment clashing, and the hallway where many goodbyes were exchanged.

Born into a medical family, Jiyan became his mother's assistant at the age of 10. He excelled at medical skills and was popular among patients, not only for his expertise, but also for his great ability to soothe their upsets and cater to their needs.

Despite his exceptional medical prowess, there were still some lives that Jiyan couldn't bring back from the jaws of death‚Äîthe last patient he couldn't save was Beiwang, his friend and mentor, who was heavily injured by Tacet Discords.

Beiwang was initially known to Jiyan as the latter's patient, among many other Midnight Rangers who had to visit a doctor after fighting the frequent Tacet Discord tides plaguing the land.

Beiwang was impressed by Jiyan's intellect and intuition, leading him to share details of the Midnight Rangers' marches and provide military instruction. Conversely, Jiyan actively contributed his analytical skills to strategy discussions, despite never experiencing battle firsthand. His unique perspectives injected vitality into their conversations, invigorating Beiwang's perspectives with a fresh outlook.

Beiwang's passing ignited a transformative spark in Jiyan‚Äîhis wistfulness, frustration, and regret turned into his strength to wield the lance on the battlefield.

Jiyan began to realize that the Lament is such a deep-seated disease in the world's veins that not even the most sophisticated medical instrument or the most adept surgeon could remove it. This realization drove him to cure the world in another way‚Äîhe took up arms and fought the Tacet Discords head-on, with unwavering resolve.

Now, only the gourd-shaped pill case on his belt loop indicates that he was once a doctor. Speculations abound about the contents of the case, with some claiming he uses sugar pearls to comfort children and others saying he drinks from it after battles.

If someone asks Jiyan about it, he would answer frankly, "Just some common medicines, in case someone needs them."

Stories.Title: The Temporary Team
Stories.Content:
Amidst the lively Jinzhou Riverside Games, a group of young men stood together.

"Here's the thing. Our captain's got an urgent matter to attend to, so we're one man short for the race. If you don't join us, we might have to forfeit."

"Please, please help us. We've been training so hard for the Gulpuff Relay. So please..."

"Yeah, please, Jiyan!" they chorused, their urgency palpable.

Standing at the center was a bright-eyed young man. Meeting their sincere gaze, he nodded in agreement. Therefore, a temporary team was formed.

The young man asked about each teammate's conditions and the relay order. Then, he decided to adjust the strategy and take on the anchor leg himself.

The Games, initially held to relieve the tension of Jinzhou people after their first triumph over the Tacet Discord Outbreaks, had evolved into a major event in Jinzhou, in which the Gulpuff Relay was one of the biggest highlights.

The whistle blew. The relay racers charged forward, skillfully evading obstacles as they piloted their Gulpuffs. Crowds of cheering audience lined the banks.

However, a mistake occurred during the baton exchange between the first and second runners, leading the temporary team to lag far behind.

"Oops, looks like this team's hit a little snag! As a temporary team, their teamwork might be a bit rusty. Pity for them!"

The commentator then shifted his attention to the top three contenders.

Amidst the cheers, the race reached its climax as the final runner of the temporary team swiftly closed the gap with their opponents, unnoticed by everyone.

"Oh man! Look at the temporary team! There was a hiccup earlier, but now the last runner is overtaking! There's a key curve ahead... Wha-what's happening? He's overtaking everyone on the curve! That's absolutely amazing!"

Undisturbed by the noise and excitement of the audience, he kept his eyes locked on the finish line. A single thought was driving him forward‚Äîfaster, just a little faster. His heart pounded, drowning out the loud cheers.

As confetti descended with a loud bang, the cacophony of sounds once again poured into his ears.

They won!

"Who could've imagined this temporary team would break the record! Congratulations to the young lads!"

His teammates swarmed him in excitement, surrounding the young man. Raising the weighty trophy, they vowed to team up again for the next Games.

Words.Title: Thoughts: I
Words.Content: I have long been stationed in the borderlands, with little knowledge of entertainment or places of leisure. However, if you are looking for tactics against <te href=850081>Tacet Discords</te> or beautiful natural vistas, I can provide some suggestions.

Words.Title: Thoughts: II
Words.Content: While the borderlands cannot rival the city's clamor and glamor, they do possess their unique charm. Should you find time, I suggest you come and witness the full moon and twinkling stars that grace the tranquil night skies. Rest assured, your safety will not be a concern; I will be there with you.

Words.Title: Thoughts: III
Words.Content: The <te href=850086>Midnight Rangers</te> are a source of solace for many, while I see them as a scalpel, with the duty of eradicating maladies. Me? I am the hand that guides this scalpel, I suppose.

Words.Title: Thoughts: IV
Words.Content: Soldiers of the <te href=850086>Midnight Rangers</te> have entrusted their lives to me. Therefore, every time I wield the scalpel, I must do so with absolute precision so as not to betray their trust. One day, this scalpel will eradicate all <te href=850081>Tacet Discords</te>, and when that moment arrives, I hope you can witness it with me.

Words.Title: Thoughts: V
Words.Content: Flowers in the Knell Square are planted to honor the deceased. These flowers are of a unique variety, and they require significant attention. Here is a cultivation guide. If I fail to keep my promise of witnessing humanity's victory with you, please plant one of these flowers there for me.

Words.Title: Jiyan's Hobby
Words.Content: Though I no longer practice medicine, I still discuss medical knowledge with my mother in my spare time. This gourd-shaped pill case is a gift from her the year I joined the <te href=850086>Midnight Rangers</te>.

Words.Title: Jiyan's Trouble
Words.Content: In just a few days, a thin layer of dust has collected on my desk. Cleaning is not a challenge, but consistency is.

Words.Title: Favorite Food
Words.Content: Jinzhou Stew is renowned for its wide variety of ingredients and easy preparation, making it a beloved homemade dish in <te href=850091>Jinzhou</te>. Having been stationed in the borderlands for most of my time, I sometimes miss that taste.

Words.Title: Disliked Food
Words.Content: In <te href=850091>Jinzhou</te>, there is a vegetable known as "Bittberry". It possesses a bitter and slightly astringent flavor, and is renowned for its detoxifying properties. When I was young, my mother was somehow convinced "those who can endure bitterness will rise above others." She frequently incorporated this vegetable into our meals. I must confess that its taste was far from pleasant. However, now serving in the army, I have grown accustomed to its flavor. After all, resources are scarce, and it is crucial not to squander them.

Words.Title: Ideals
Words.Content: If one day, the borderlands no longer need a general, I suppose my wish will have come true.

Words.Title: Chat: I
Words.Content: This spear was modeled after the weapon of Captain Beiwang, bearing the significance of quelling chaos and warding off external threats.

Words.Title: Chat: II
Words.Content: My family has been in the medical profession for generations. I once aspired to follow in their footsteps, saving lives and providing care. However, I soon realized that a doctor could never fully alleviate the pain caused by the <te href=850081>Tacet Discords</te>. It was this realization that led me to join the <te href=850086>Midnight Rangers</te>. Over the years, I have found my way of bringing solace to the world.

Words.Title: Birthday Wishes
Words.Content: I have worn this vambrace since my first battle. It saved my life countless times. A vambrace like this is believed to bring good luck, ensuring the safe return of soldiers. Though it may show signs of wear, I wish to pass on this luck to you. Additionally, I have prepared a few travel essentials that I hope will prove useful. Happy birthday.

Words.Title: Self-Introduction
Words.Content: Jiyan, of the Midnight Rangers. Protecting our lands and people is my solemn duty. Should you encounter any difficulties here, I will do my utmost to help.

Words.Title: Join Team: I
Words.Content: Should you find yourself lost, follow the banner of the Qingloong.

Words.Title: Join Team: II
Words.Content: When danger arises, take cover behind me.

Words.Title: Join Team: III
Words.Content: The battlefield is dynamic. Do not let your guard down.

Words.Title: Ascension: I
Words.Content: I can sense an improvement in my strength. I suppose you are well-versed in the art of training, too?

Words.Title: Ascension: II
Words.Content: So you have opted for a prudent strategy this time. Next time, maybe we can consider something more unconventional.

Words.Title: Ascension: III
Words.Content: Remarkable strategy. Your insight provides me with unique and refreshing perspectives that I have not considered before.

Words.Title: Ascension: IV
Words.Content: With your bold plan, my Qingloong has gained more momentum on the battlefield. I appreciate your assistance.

Words.Content: Extra supplies.

Words.Title: About Mortefi
Words.Content: Others often perceive Mortefi as arrogant and unapproachable, but, in fact, he is not that hard to talk to. Remember to be direct with him, as trying to be overly polite and subtle may only lead to misunderstandings.

Words.Title: About Jinhsi
Words.Content: The "battle" Magistrate Jinhsi has been taking on may prove more complicated than our situation in the borderlands: stipulating rules, overseeing trade, ensuring the well-being of the people, and managing the city's functioning all demand her coordination and judgement. Every time I return to <te href=850091>Jinzhou</te>, I can feel the city's vibrancy and enthusiasm, all thanks to her meticulous governance.

Words.Title: About Taoqi
Words.Content: Taoqi... Though our views on loose management don't always align, I am able to focus on the front lines without any worries, thanks to her effective leadership in maintaining <te href=850091>Jinzhou</te>'s fortifications.

Words.Title: About Yangyang
Words.Content: She can perceive minute changes in the surroundings from the Streams, but there is a limit to the amount of information a single person can take in. Excessive use of this ability might add to her burden, and I hope she won't strain herself.

Words.Title: About Baizhi
Words.Content: Many stumble through life directionless, without ever finding a purpose. Baizhi is among the rare few who have found their calling, and she is willing to give up anything for the truth she pursues.

Words.Title: About Chixia
Words.Content: That energetic and passionate <te href=850087>Patroller</te>? Yes, I have heard of her. She has been devoting her time to protecting the dreams of children in <te href=850091>Jinzhou</te>.

Words.Title: About Aalto
Words.Content: Fog can be an enemy to soldiers on the march, as it limits visibility and complicates situational awareness. However, deploying fog strategically can be an effective move on the battlefield. I have had the opportunity to work with Aalto before, and he is an interesting person indeed.

Words.Title: About Encore
Words.Content: Are you referring to the little girl who is always seen by Aalto's side? I have met her once. She and Aalto complement each other perfectly, personality wise.

Words.Title: Greeting
Words.Content: I have never regretted braving the long night.

Words.Title: Enemies Near
Words.Content: Stay sharp.

Words.Title: Sensor
Words.Content: Approach with tact.

Words.Title: Supply Chest: II
Words.Content: For emergencies.

Words.Title: Supply Chest: III
Words.Content: Wouldn't hurt to be more prepared.

Words.Title: Ascension: V
Words.Content: Commanding an army is not a simple task, and sometimes I find myself questioning my own decisions. Going forward, with you staying by my side, I should feel more at ease.

Words.Title: Intro Skill: II
Words.Content: Ready for battle.

Goods.Title: The Art of War
Goods.Content:
"A general is a man of wisdom, faith, benevolence, courage, and discipline." 
One needs more than invincible strength to lead an army. It's more about a good mind of leadership and careful planning. As a result, Jiyan's desk is always organized with books on warfare, which are filled with notes reflecting his own strategies.

Goods.Title: Medicine Box
Goods.Content: Jiyan's enlistment in the army came with a gift from his mother‚Äîa medicine box shaped like a Terminal. She feared he would become a killer on the battlefield and reminded him of his role as a healer. He later used it to carry necessary medicines, just in case.

Goods.Title: A Corner of Jinzhou
Goods.Content: On an ordinary, everyday afternoon in <te href=850091>Jinzhou</te>, the sun was shining through the clear sky and spreading to thousands of homes, and Jiyan couldn't help but take pictures of the scene. The soldiers' sacrifices hold even greater significance against this tranquil backdrop.
